OL,3,CFree stays offered at more than 150
OL,4,CEuropean marinas
OL,6,FGuernsey Ports is offering mooring
OL,7,Fholders the chance to stay for free in
OL,8,Fmore than 150 European marinas.
OL,10,FIt is part of a new reciprocal
OL,11,Fagreement under Pass-Ports Escales
OL,12,Fthat allows them two complimentary
OL,13,Fnights in participating ports across
OL,14,Fthe UK, France, Belgium, the
OL,15,FNetherlands, Portugal and Spain for up
OL,16,Fto ten days per season.
OL,18,FVisitor fees are covered by the home
OL,19,Fmarina and hundreds of people have
OL,20,Falready taken advantage of the deal
OL,21,Fwhen docking in Guernsey this summer.
