OL,6,FGuernsey's Assistant Harbourmaster
OL,7,FKieran Higgs says the new arrangement
OL,8,Fis gives mooring holder greater value
OL,9,Ffor money
OL,11,Fwhile also promoting the island to a
OL,12,Fwider audience and attracting new
OL,14,Fvisitors.
OL,16,FHe explains: "This has helped put
OL,17,FGuernsey on the map and promote our
OL,18,Fexcellent cruising grounds to a whole
OL,19,Fnew audience.
