OL,6,F"We are already seeing the benefits of
OL,7,Fthat. So far this season, we have
OL,8,Fwelcomed just over 300 visiting
OL,9,Fvessels under the Pass-Ports Escales
OL,10,Fscheme.
OL,12,F"A number of first-time leisure
OL,13,Fvisitors from Europe have gone on to
OL,14,Fstay longer than two nights, while it
OL,15,Fhas also prompted some previous
OL,16,Fvisitors to return to our waters
OL,17,Fagain."
